{{otheruses4|the werewolf|the city|Vehlarr (city)}}
'''Vehlarr''' was a natural [[werewolf]] and accomplished [[sorcerer]] who was favored by [[Malar]] and [[Sehanine]]. With their help, he organized the packs of werewolves in the [[Wood of Sharp Teeth]] and formed the city of [[Vehlarr (city)|Vehlarr]] within the forest.{{Cite web/The Search for the Circle of Vehlarr/Part Six}}
